# defination of score.sentiment function
score.sentiment=function(data_c,pos_words,neg_words,.progress='none'){
  
  score_words<-lapply(data_c,function(data_c,pos_words,neg_words){
    data_c = gsub('[[:punct:]]',' ',data_c) # removing punctuation
    data_c = gsub('[[:cntrl:]]',' ',data_c) 
    data_c = gsub('\\d+',' ',data_c) # removing decimal no
    data_c = gsub('\n',' ',data_c) # removing new_line
    data_c = gsub(pattern = "\\W",replace =" ",data_c)
    data_c = tolower(data_c) # convert to lower_case
    data_c = gsub(pattern = "\\b[A-z]\\b(1)",replace=" ",data_c)
   
    word.list<-str_split(data_c,'\\s+')
    clean_words = unlist(word.list)
    
    # matching of words
    pos_match = match(clean_words, pos_words)
    neg_match = match(clean_words, neg_words)
    pos_match = !is.na(pos_match)
    neg_match = !is.na(neg_match)
    pos_score = sum(pos_match)
    neg_score = sum(neg_match)
    score = sum(pos_match) - sum(neg_match)
    score_list = c(score, pos_score, neg_score)
    return (score_list)
    
  },pos_words,neg_words )
  
  # extracting score , positive & negative words
  score_final = lapply(score_words, `[[`, 1)
  positive_score = lapply(score_words, `[[`, 2)
  negative_score = lapply(score_words, `[[`, 3)
  
  scores_data_frame = data.frame(score = score_final, text=data_c)
  positive_data_frame = data.frame(Positive = positive_score, text=data_c)
  negative_data_frame = data.frame(Negative = negative_score, text=data_c)
  
  data_frame_list = list(scores_data_frame, positive_data_frame, negative_data_frame)
  return(data_frame_list)
  
}

# top 10 hashing 
tweet_dfh<-twListToDF(tweets)
tweet_dfh_text<-tweet_dfh$text
hash_pattern = "#[[:alpha:]]+"
find_hash<-grep(x = tweet_dfh_text, pattern = hash_pattern)

match_hash = gregexpr(pattern = hash_pattern,text = tweet_dfh_text[find_hash])
extract_hashing = regmatches(x = tweet_dfh_text[find_hash], m = match_hash) #the actual hashtags are stored here

tw_df_th = data.frame(table(tolower(unlist(extract_hashing)))) #dataframe formed with var1(hashtag), freq of hashtag
colnames(tw_df_th) = c("tag","freq")
tw_df_th =tw_df_th[order(tw_df_th$freq,decreasing = T),]
#tw_df_th

data_head_hf = head(tw_df_th,50)
